writ lint --cloud               AI scoring via enwrit.com API only (requires login)
writ lint --local               AI scoring via your configured local model (writ model set local)
writ lint --local-model         Bundled writ-lint-0.8B model (auto-downloaded, no setup needed)
writ lint --code                Force Tier 1 code-only scoring (deterministic)
writ lint --score               Output headline score only (machine-readable)
writ lint --quiet               Output score + dimension table only (no issues/suggestions)
writ connect                    Interactive peer setup wizard for real repos
